## Limitations
The report is based on available data and publications up to October 2023. The dynamic nature of economic conditions means that the effects of inflation can vary over time and across different regions. Additionally, the analysis is limited to the perspectives and insights provided by the selected sources, which may not cover all possible scenarios or outcomes related to rising inflation.

